The non-Newtonian fluid inside the cavity obeys the Ostwald-de Waele power law model, based on the shear stress tensor:

(12)


\matrix{ {{\tau _{xx}} = 2{\mu _{nf}}\displaystyle{{\partial u} \over {\partial x}}\; } \cr }
τxx=2μnf∂u∂x


(13)


\matrix{ {{\tau _{yy}} = 2{\mu _{nf}}\displaystyle{{\partial v} \over {\partial y}}\; } \cr }
τyy=2μnf∂v∂y


(14)


\matrix{ {{\tau _{xy}} = {\tau _{yx}} = {\mu _{nf}}\left( {\displaystyle{{\partial u} \over {\partial y}} + \; \displaystyle{{\partial v} \over {\partial x}}} \right)\; } \cr }
τxy=τyx=μnf(∂u∂y+∂v∂x)
